      <span class=3D"node">router =E2=86=92 controller =E2=86=92 validator =
=E2=86=92 model</span><span class=3D"arrow">=E2=86=92</span>
      <span class=3D"node">better-sqlite3</span><span class=3D"arrow">=E2=
=86=92</span>
      <span class=3D"node">tasks.db (WAL)</span>
    </div>
    <p>Two independent apps (<code>client/</code>, <code>client/</code> sep=
arate <code>package.json</code>) run together only via a root <code>concurr=
ently</code> script (<code>npm run dev</code>). In dev, the client never ta=
lks cross-origin =E2=80=94 Vite's proxy forwards <code>/api/*</code> to <co=
de>localhost:3000</code>, so the browser only ever sees same-origin request=
s. <code>cors()</code> on the server is still enabled with no allowlist (op=
en to any origin), which only matters if something calls the API directly i=
nstead of through the proxy/built app.</p>
  </section>

  <section id=3D"backend">
    <h2>Backend deep dive</h2>

    <h3>Request pipeline (server/src/index.ts)</h3>
    <p>Middleware order, top to bottom =E2=80=94 order matters here:</p>
    <ol>
      <li><code>requestLogger</code> =E2=80=94 logs method/path/status/dura=
tion on the response <code>finish</code> event (status isn't known until th=
en, so it can't log up front)</li>
      <li><code>cors()</code>, <code>express.json()</code></li>
      <li><code>/health</code> =E2=80=94 trivial liveness check</li>
      <li><code>/api/tasks</code> =E2=86=92 <code>burstLimiter</code> =E2=
=86=92 <code>sustainedLimiter</code> =E2=86=92 task router</li>
      <li><code>errorHandler</code> =E2=80=94 registered <strong>last</stro=
ng>, on purpose: Express only routes errors to middleware defined after the=
 throwing handler</li>
    </ol>
    <p>A separate <code>server.on("error")</code> handler catches startup f=
ailures like <code>EADDRINUSE</code> so a taken port fails with a clear mes=
sage instead of an opaque crash.</p>

    <h3>REST surface</h3>
    <div class=3D"table-wrap">
    <table>
      <tbody><tr><th>Method</th><th>Path</th><th>Purpose</th><th>Notes</th>=
</tr>
      <tr><td><span class=3D"method m-get">GET</span></td><td><code>/api/ta=
sks</code></td><td>List all tasks</td><td>No query params =E2=80=94 full ta=
